Sentencas: Anode-supported solid oxide fuel cells accumulating more than 700 h of stable operation on dry ethanol with high current output are reported.
Titulo: Durable direct ethanol anode-supported solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: A highly active ceria-based catalytic layer deposited onto the anode efficiently converts the primary fuel into hydrogen using the electrochemically generated steam.
Titulo: Durable direct ethanol anode-supported solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: On the other hand, standard fuel cells without the catalytic layer collapse because of carbon deposit formation within the initial 5 h of operation with ethanol.
Titulo: Durable direct ethanol anode-supported solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The nanostructured ceria-based catalyst forms a continuous porous layer (similar to 25 mu m thick) over the Ni-based anode support that has no apparent influence on the fuel cell operation and prevents carbon deposit formation.
Titulo: Durable direct ethanol anode-supported solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: Moreover, the catalytic layer promotes overall steam reforming reactions of ethanol that result in similar current outputs in both hydrogen and ethanol fuels.
Titulo: Durable direct ethanol anode-supported solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The stability of single cells, with relatively large active area (8 cm(2)), confirms the feasibility of a catalytic layer for internal reforming of biofuels in solid oxide fuel cells.
Titulo: Durable direct ethanol anode-supported solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The experimental results provide a significant step towards the practical application of direct ethanol solid oxide fuel cells.
Titulo: Durable direct ethanol anode-supported solid oxide fuel cell
